content: You're welcome! For the 9/11 Memorial and Museum, you can take the subway to the World Trade Center Station, which is served by the E subway line. Alternatively, you can take the A, C, J, Z, 2, 3, 4, or 5 subway line to Fulton Street Station and then walk about 10 minutes to the museum. When you exit the subway and surface onto the street level, you'll see signs pointing you towards the 9/11 Memorial and Museum.
